-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PART - A

Connecting to your GIT account
1) git config --global user.email "sonawanesarvesh@gmail.com"
2) git config --global user.name "sonawanesarvesh"

Connecting your project folder with GIT
3) git init

Git Status
4) git status

connecting all files to git
5) git add -A

Enter commit desciption (snapshot description)
6) git commit -m "Added intex.html and custom.css"

connecting project with gitHub
(go to github - creare repository - learngit)

7) git remote add origin https://github.com/sonawanesarvesh/learngit.git

pushing code to github
8) git push -u origin master

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PART - B
Adding new user
New user will pull / clone github
1) git clone https://github.com/sonawanesarvesh/learngit.git

