PART - C

1) get list of branches
git branch

2) create new branch
git branch new_branch

3) switch to new branch from master branch
git checkout new_feature

Now developer can work on this new branch

suppose developer have added new file local projects folder
now user want to commit this new file 

now after committing new file, user need to merge new_feature branch with main branch

git branch new_feature